---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CompoundCalculator from '../../components/CompoundCalculator';
---

<Layout
  title="적립식 복리 계산기 · Snowballlab"
  description="적립식(매월 납입) 복리 계산기"
>
  <section class="space-y-4">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Recurring Calculator</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">적립식 복리 계산기</h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      매월 납입하는 적립식 투자 시나리오를 계산합니다. 월/연 보기로 결과를 확인할 수 있습니다.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-6 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/40">
    <CompoundCalculator client:load mode="recurring" />
  </section>
</Layout>
